Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:06.64,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.11,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's stage is a white{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10} san{\r\be10}dy beach!\NCouples come in varieties!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.68,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Saturday and Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You will?! Really?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:04.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just talking to a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:30.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This Saturday and Sunday! You didn't have any plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:34.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really beautiful hotel and its private beach is the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it costs the greatest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first break in a while, so I'd rather drink and sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm pretty sure you drink and sleep even when you {\i1}are{\i0} working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I already promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no one! Nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come swimming too, right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:04.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Don't teach him to be lazy at such a young age!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:09.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the hotel's beach is filled with sexy women in swimsuits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:13.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's brimming with college girls and female office workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's she saying? Ran is usually {\i1}against{\i0} that kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:24.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I {\i1}have{\i0} been working a lot lately. Recuperation might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:36.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, now! The old guy's the same as ever, but what's up with Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The ocean's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sexy sea is calling for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:56.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Izu\NQueen Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel definitely lives up to its reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Let's hurry and check in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- You've reserved two rooms.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:28.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We don't need separate rooms. Wouldn't a suite be cheaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:31.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd only get in the way later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing! Let's just{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge and hurry to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Sexy girls are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Too strange. Something is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So much sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah! Here it is, Dad! The swimsuit I bought yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:02.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud! I don't want anyone to know I have annoyances!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhh, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hey there, nice-bodied girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can rub that oil on you if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eri? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a wonderful coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:33.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're true lovebirds! It's like you make a perfect pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ran, don't tell me...\N- ...you plotted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Plotted what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you got separate rooms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:48.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Geez. It's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop being angry, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for secretly bringing you together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:07.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy the Izu ocean more! Okay? Okay? Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}was{\i0} enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:17.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until a hag showed up, wearing a swimsuit that didn't match her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:26.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and who was drooling and howling at the sight of that hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Dad! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:40.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just embarrassed! He hasn't seen you in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:48.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, he looks like a petty-minded man who can't ever concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not wearing your wedding ring? You usually do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:07:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's on purpose. I was testing him to see if he'd notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:05.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there would still be hope if he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:12.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is a huge failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:16.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should quit with this separation and start my life over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:22.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wind up like that man, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I don't think I would ever want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What could've happened? Dad's been gone a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably back at the beach, hitting on girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky to meet the great Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:56.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor for me, too! To think I have such charming female fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:06.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably just met them after he used the bathroom! And then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his legs, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:13.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were clean before, but now there's{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d up to his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:20.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily imagine him kneeling in the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d to rub oil on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he brought them here to show off to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:27.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't tell me he actually...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:34.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should start a fan club or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:39.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:42.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran! These girls say they're fans of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with these two first! I met them on the beach just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako Toda\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kiwako Toda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Harumi Matsuzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, also a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:01.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Harumi Matsuzaki\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How cute! Is this your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:10.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's Conan, an acquaintance's kid who we're looking after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind him is my daughter, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the back is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...his ex-wife, Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:23.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You're divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not necessarily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:35.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunio Kawazu\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy your age shouldn't be messin' with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Masahiko! You say somethin', too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dear fiancée and sister are bein' fooled, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:47.21,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masahiko Matsuzaki\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:46.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You don't have to be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he seems to be a celebrity, so you can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the famous "Sleeping Kogoro" detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:02.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I knew I recognized you from somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:07.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm that well-known? I'm at a loss for words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My face gets in papers and on TV all over, so I can't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you had lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all have lunch together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:24.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a small restaurant behind this hotel. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh! Sounds good!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:43.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're all part of your school's scuba diving club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We even had a dive this morning before lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:53.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your last time diving single before the wedding next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll be diving tomorrow too, so this isn't the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:03.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was tough getting my brother into this club! He can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:05.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to swim to dive. You got an oxygen{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}k, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:15.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as a boy, Masahiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was never able to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Does that mean you two are childhood friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Childhood friends getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like my mom and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Right?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Childhood friends," huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:41.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So many a couple have been heartbroken by that sweet phrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:46.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing familiar friend {\i1}and{\i0} fantasy is the height of foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think you'll need it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ever distrust your wife, just call the Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:59.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to receive major compensation from your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:03.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when you divorce, just call the Kisaki Law Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Brrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:15.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, where's your other childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiroshi said he was gonna do some snorkeling after the dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snore- killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:26.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Diving without an air{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}k.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's diving without even eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:34.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He {\i1}is{\i0} kind of strange; he likes the ocean more than women!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if he plans to marry a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Harumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:50.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask, but could you get a fresh beach towel from our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiwako. Don't tell me you're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I suddenly want to take a dip in the ocean, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be alright drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:05.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do it today. Can't you go tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:08.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! I haven't had that much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be some light snorkeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I join you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! I want to dive by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Harumi! Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean seems to be getting rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Kiwako is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:47.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi! You're with Kawazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran into each other in the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Ito\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's diving spot was really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:59.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You didn't see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:07.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There she is! She's waving to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Something doesn't seem right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait!\N- She's drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait!\N- She's drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kiwako!\N- Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Masahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:15:00.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Get back! You can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:08.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're alright now!\N- Kiwako! Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Masahiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's here. He came to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}T-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stud! You can carry her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:36.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Masahiko! She probably just had a leg cramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}D-Don't tell me she...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. We told you not to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:49.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You can argue all you want after you're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiwako. Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might've been bitten by a sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sea snake right by us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:24.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If so, then there should be fang marks somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hand... Left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Bite marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:35.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she {\i1}was{\i0} bitten by a sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we have to tie off the affected area and suck out the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have anything to use as a tourniquet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Will a handkerchief do?!\N- Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know it was a sea snake, little...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the sea snake! It was about 40 centimeters long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong?!\N- Call an ambulance, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:09.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought you saved her from drowning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake bit Kiwako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the back of her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Those are really poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:29.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he just run off with iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tannin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Washing the wound with the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}nin in tea to neutralize the poison
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is the best emergency measure for sea snake bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the person who sucks out the poison
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will need to wash their mouth with tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:49.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how does that runt know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:52.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He's a pretty sharp boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:58.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's much more useful than we are, as we twiddle our thumbs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though shouldn't you ask why a certain former police detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't know about it instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll call the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:13.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ask the cook for some coarse tea full of{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}nin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako... Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her fiancé. Can I come with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who saw the sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what type it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The type?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:44.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a picture book in the hotel office...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:48.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then contact the hospital as soon as you know what kind it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.43,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It was this sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- A black-banded sea krait!\N- What's it doing in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:22.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sometimes show up on the Kuroshio Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just a prickly feeling and then no swelling after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:27.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so some fishermen have died without ever noticing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You let people swim in the ocean with such dangerous sea snakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishermen just happened to be bitten
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:40.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when sticking their hands in fish nets that had also caught the snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we're talking about sea snakes here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:46.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely some might suddenly attack people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:51.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These snakes are docile and never attack people on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the 22 years since this hotel was founded,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,not a single visitor has been bitten by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, do any of these sea snakes have feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Feathers? No such variety exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:15.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall seeing small feathers behind the head of the one I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:19.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed or something must've caught onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:26.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But only my daughter could remember so much from one quick look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only remember well because it was so shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:32.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you have a wonderful power of observation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a certain someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:38.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't even notice his wife's missing wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:41.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about your ring now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:51.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine she playfully stuck her hand in the snake's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll go contact the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:10.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Those fang marks were no accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:16.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Someone held the snake and forced it to bite her hand in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:20.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In which case, was it one of the people who rushed to help her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, everyone was empty-handed then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and they rushed there because Kiwako{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no one crazy enough to have a sea snake ready
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}when they don't know if someone will drown or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:40.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It'd be more natural to think she started to drown after she was bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:45.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means only Hiroshi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:49.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He was in the ocean just before she drowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:52.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so he could've had it bite her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:58.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But his emergency treatment afterward was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:04.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Would someone go that far to help someone they're trying to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:10.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In any event, one of those four people was responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You liked Kiwako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:54.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me? I can't find Kiwako's insurance card!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the towel at the bottom of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:08.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was no accident! And you're the one behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:14.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.82,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Part 2! Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:21.98,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:23.20,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's it gotta be me?!
